<style>
  .get-started-container {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #a5b4fc 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .two-column {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .column {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(165, 180, 252, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .column-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: #a5b4fc;
  }

  .requirements-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .requirement-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(165, 180, 252, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .requirement-item:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    border-color: rgba(165, 180, 252, 0.3);
  }

  .requirement-number {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: rgba(165, 180, 252, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #a5b4fc;
  }

  .requirement-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .requirement-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .requirement-description {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .steps-container {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .step-card {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step-number {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(165, 180, 252, 0.3) 0%, rgba(147, 51, 234, 0.3) 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .step-content {
    margin-left: 3.25rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .code-snippet {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    border: 1px solid rgba(165, 180, 252, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Inconsolata', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .code-comment {
    color: rgba(134, 239, 172, 0.6);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .code-key {
    color: #a5b4fc;
  }

  .code-value {
    color: #86efac;
  }

  .code-function {
    color: #fbbf24;
  }

  .link {
    color: #a5b4fc;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .link:hover {
    color: #c7d2fe;
  }

  .pro-tip {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1) 0%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.875rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .pro-tip-icon {
    color: #22c55e;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .pro-tip-content {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>

<div class="get-started-container" id="get-started">
  <h2 class="section-title">Get Started with Spotlight</h2>
  
  <div class="two-column">
    
    
    <!-- Quick Start Column -->
    <div class="column">
    
      <div class="steps-container">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-header">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h4 class="step-title">Install a Sentry SDK</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <p>If you don't have one already, install a Sentry SDK for your framework.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-header">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h4 class="step-title">Configure Sentry.init()</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <p>Add Spotlight to your Sentry configuration:</p>
            <div class="code-snippet">
              <span class="code-function">Sentry.init</span>({'{'}<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-key">dsn</span>: <span class="code-value">"your-dsn"</span>,<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-key">spotlight</span>: <span class="code-value">true</span>, <span class="code-comment">// Enable Spotlight</span><br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-key">integrations</span>: [<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-comment">// For frontend apps, add:</span><br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-function">Sentry.browserApiErrorsIntegration</span>(),<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;],<br>
              {'}'});
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
              For frontend frameworks, consider adding the 
              <a href="/reference/console/" class="link">Console Integration</a> 
              to capture console logs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-header">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h4 class="step-title">Enable Logging</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <p>To get the most out of Spotlight, enable logging in your SDK:</p>
            <div class="code-snippet">
              <span class="code-function">Sentry.init</span>({'{'}<br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-comment">// ... other config</span><br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-key">tracesSampleRate</span>: <span class="code-value">1.0</span>, <span class="code-comment">// Capture all traces in dev</span><br>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="code-key">debug</span>: <span class="code-value">true</span>, <span class="code-comment">// Enable debug mode</span><br>
              {'}'});
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
              Learn more about 
              <a href="/reference/sentry/#enabling-logs" class="link">enabling logs in your SDK</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pro-tip">
        <svg class="pro-tip-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
        </svg>
        <div class="pro-tip-content">
          <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Spotlight runs automatically when you use <code>npx @spotlightjs/spotlight --stdio-mcp</code>. 
          The overlay will appear in your browser when errors or traces are captured!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
